============================================================
CONFIG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Update root `.env.example`:

SOVEREIGN_MODE_ENABLED=true
SOVEREIGN_FAIL_CLOSED=true
DEFAULT_DATA_REGION=local
ALLOWED_DATA_REGIONS=local,us,eu,apac
DISALLOWED_DATA_REGIONS=
DATA_RESIDENCY_ENFORCEMENT_ENABLED=true
CROSS_REGION_SYNC_ENABLED=false
CROSS_REGION_SYNC_DRY_RUN=true

SOVEREIGN_PROFILE_DEFAULT=local
SOVEREIGN_POLICY_BUNDLE_ENABLED=true
SOVEREIGN_COMPLIANCE_DASHBOARD_ENABLED=true

CUSTOMER_MANAGED_KEYS_ENABLED=true
KMS_PROVIDER=mock
KMS_DRY_RUN=true
KMS_KEY_REF=
KMS_REQUIRE_CUSTOMER_APPROVAL=true

EDGE_RUNNERS_ENABLED=true
EDGE_RUNNER_DRY_RUN=true
EDGE_RUNNER_REGISTRATION_ENABLED=true
EDGE_JOB_DISPATCH_ENABLED=true
EDGE_JOB_DISPATCH_DRY_RUN=true
EDGE_OFFLINE_SYNC_ENABLED=true
EDGE_OFFLINE_SYNC_DRY_RUN=true
EDGE_SYNC_CONFLICT_POLICY=manual_review

ONPREM_APPLIANCE_ENABLED=true
ONPREM_APPLIANCE_BUNDLE_DRY_RUN=true
ONPREM_EXCLUDE_SECRETS=true
ONPREM_REQUIRE_ADMIN=true

GLOBAL_OPS_ENABLED=true
GLOBAL_ROLLOUT_ENABLED=true
GLOBAL_ROLLOUT_DRY_RUN=true
GLOBAL_ROLLOUT_REQUIRE_APPROVAL=true

RESELLER_OPS_ENABLED=true
RESELLER_BILLING_AUTHORITY_REQUIRED=true

REGIONAL_MARKETPLACE_ENABLED=true
REGIONAL_MARKETPLACE_FAIL_CLOSED=true

REGIONAL_BILLING_METADATA_ENABLED=true
REGIONAL_TAX_METADATA_DRY_RUN=true

GLOBAL_SUPPORT_ESCALATION_ENABLED=true
CROSS_REGION_OBSERVABILITY_ENABLED=true
CROSS_REGION_OBSERVABILITY_REDACTED=true

Rules:
- Sovereign mode must fail closed when enabled.
- Cross-region sync is disabled by default.
- KMS integration is mock/dry-run by default.
- Edge jobs are dry-run by default.
- On-prem appliance excludes secrets by default.
- Global rollout is dry-run and approval-gated by default.
- Regional marketplace must block uncertified or region-disallowed listings.
- Cross-region observability must show summaries only, not raw tenant data.
- No secret values may appear in configs, logs, reports, bundles, frontend, desktop, mobile, or docs.

