============================================================
API RESPONSE FORMAT
============================================================

All endpoints must use standard response shape:

Success:

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Error:

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Human readable message"
  },
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Required error codes:

- SOVEREIGN_DISABLED
- REGION_NOT_FOUND
- REGION_NOT_ALLOWED
- RESIDENCY_POLICY_BLOCKED
- SOVEREIGN_PROFILE_NOT_FOUND
- KMS_NOT_CONFIGURED
- KMS_KEY_REF_INVALID
- POLICY_BUNDLE_NOT_FOUND
- EDGE_DISABLED
- EDGE_RUNNER_NOT_FOUND
- EDGE_RUNNER_REVOKED
- EDGE_JOB_NOT_FOUND
- EDGE_JOB_BLOCKED
- EDGE_SYNC_BLOCKED
- EDGE_SYNC_CONFLICT
- ONPREM_BUNDLE_NOT_FOUND
- ONPREM_SECRET_CONFIRMATION_REQUIRED
- GLOBAL_OPS_DISABLED
- ACCOUNT_NOT_FOUND
- RESELLER_NOT_FOUND
- RESELLER_AUTHORITY_REQUIRED
- REGIONAL_MARKETPLACE_BLOCKED
- REGIONAL_BILLING_METADATA_ONLY
- GLOBAL_ROLLOUT_BLOCKED
- CROSS_REGION_OBSERVABILITY_REDACTED
- TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED

